Class ZombieGameMapFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.ZombieGameMapFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompoundMapFactory, TownMapFactory

    public abstract class ZombieGameMapFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that defines the models (size, terrain, actors etc.) of the maps in the Zombie game world. Factory for creating maps of the game world.
    Author:
    Kee Pei Jiin
